headline: WEC Energy: Q1 Earnings Snapshot
summary: On a per-share basis, the Milwaukee-based company said it had net income of $2.27. The results surpassed Wall Street expectations. The average estimate of four analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for earnings of $2.19 per share.

headline: WEC Energy Group reports first-quarter results
summary: WEC Energy Group (NYSE: WEC) today reported net income of $724.2 million, or $2.27 per share, for the first quarter of 2025. This compares to earnings of $622.3 million, or $1.97 per share, for last year's first quarter.
